-| Mutation | Idempotent? | Evidence |
-|----------|-------------|----------|
-| `refresh_program_state` â†’ stale lane to Failed | **No** | Sets `last_finished_at = Some(now)`; re-running would set different timestamp |
-| `run_fabro` â†’ spawn worker | **Yes** | Uses UUID-based run ID; duplicate spawns would have different IDs |
